headline: Renewables Emerge as Key to Meet AI-Driven Energy Demand
summary: NextEra Energy asserts that renewable energy sources are crucial for addressing the increasing U.S. power demand driven by AI and manufacturing growth, positioning them as a vital bridge until new gas and nuclear capacities are developed.
